GE Code challenge instructions

Write a program that does the following:

1. Will read the text from the two provided files (great_expectations.txt, war_and_peace.txt)
2. cleans the text of special characters
3. removes common stopwords from the file (included in stopwords.txt)
4. counts the usage frequency of unique words
5. reports the top 10 words

Order of importance when writing code:

1. functionality
2. code maintainability
3. speed

Send back the source code with instructions on how to build and run, along with the output for both files